title: Sorocza Nóżka
summary: Sorocza Nóżka [sɔˈrɔt͡ʂa ˈnuʂka] is a village in the administrative district of Gmina Hajnówka, within Hajnówka County, Podlaskie Voivodeship, in north-eastern Poland, close to the border with Belarus. It lies approximately 8 kilometres (5 mi) north-east of Hajnówka and 47 km (29 mi) south-east of the regional capital Białystok.
content:
Sorocza Nóżka [sɔˈrɔt͡ʂa ˈnuʂka] is a village in the administrative district of Gmina Hajnówka, within Hajnówka County, Podlaskie Voivodeship, in north-eastern Poland, close to the border with Belarus. It lies approximately 8 kilometres (5 mi) north-east of Hajnówka and 47 km (29 mi) south-east of the regional capital Białystok.
